title: House Republicans say no collusion between Trump, Russia
text:
House Republicans say no collusion between Trump, Russia 9:27pm EDT - 01:35 
House Intelligence Committee Republicans said on Monday the panel had finished conducting interviews in its investigation of Russia and the 2016 U.S. election, and found no collusion between President Donald Trump’s associates and Moscow’s efforts to influence the campaign. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
